imdb.plot outline: Underground rapper, Bookie, returns home after a six-month road tour to find drama going on since his departure. His baby mother, Honey, has been cheating on him with a guy named Rico. Honey ends the affair by showing up at Rico's house unannounced and cursing him out in front of his girlfriend. After Rico's girlfriend ends their relationship due to Honey ousting their affair, Rico vows revenge on Honey and Bookie's relationship. Meanwhile Bookie's best friend, Rodney, who is an aspiring preacher becomes the understudy of one of Atlanta's well-known mega pastors, Bishop Bobby Bling Bling. Rodney has a falling out with Bishop Bling Bling, after the Bishops repeated advances towards Rodney's girlfriend, Peaches. Bookie continues his quest for super stardom while dealing with the struggles of maintaining a healthy relationship in an unhealthy environment.
